'''馬克·紹爾'''（Mark Schauer；{{bd|1961年|10月2日}}）是[[美國|美國]]的一位政治人物<ref name=MIManual2005>{{cite book | author = Michigan Legislative Service Bureau | title = Michigan Manual 2005-2006 | publisher = Legislative Council, State of Michigan | year = 2006 | location = Lansing, MI | pages = 149 | url = http://www.legislature.mi.gov/(S(khwxmyqj3u0soobvfl4d0b55))/mileg.aspx?page=MM2005-2006&chapter=3 | chapter = Biographical Sketches - Senate | chapterurl = http://www.legislature.mi.gov/documents/publications/manual/2005-2006/2005-MM-0149-0149-Schauer.pdf | ISBN = 1-878210-06-8 | accessdate = 2007-06-29 | archive-date = 2019-10-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191018152646/http://www.legislature.mi.gov/(S(l53n5udm00aiyct3jmujykj1))/mileg.aspx?page=MM2005-2006 | dead-url = no }}</ref>
<ref name=MSD>{{cite web  | author = Michigan Senate Democrats  | title = Michigan Senate Democrats: About Mark Schauer  | year = 2007  | url = http://www.senate.mi.gov/schauer/about.php  | accessdate = 2007-06-29  | deadurl = yes  | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071027132207/http://www.senate.mi.gov/schauer/about.php  | archivedate = 2007-10-27  }}</ref>。在2009年至2011年期間，他是密西根州第4選舉區選出的美國眾議院議員。他的黨籍是[[民主黨_(美國)|民主黨]]。在1997年至2002年，他曾是密歇根州眾議院議員。2003年至2009年期間，他是密歇根州參議院議員。

